{"tid":1168891,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"本田原廠激改兩部梯R","createTime":"2019-05-24T04:06:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T05:08:51.000Z","uid":236926,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"55fb31acd284e9769add2dfb581d0ac499ca6f2a","tid":1168891,"uid":236926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T04:06:47.000Z","msg":"[From MenClub Auto]<br />\n<br />\n本田(Honda)英國在SMMT Test Day公開兩部概念車，一部Team Dynamics Motorsport道路合法版本，2.0公升Turbo引擎經remap，配上新intercooler、排氣系統，馬力提升94hp至400hp，扭力500Nm，還升級Eibach Pro performance springs、可調校anti-roll bars及後camber arms、19吋合金輪圈配Dunlop跑胎。<br />\n另一部則是Honda Civic Type R OveRland，由Ralph Hosier Engineering製作，車身升高4吋，配255/55 BF Goodrich輪胎。不過兩部車也暫時沒計劃量產，但Team Dynamics及Ralph Hosier Engineering都說有興趣的車迷可以找他們商量商量。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7g4x9RC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7g4x9RC.jpg&h=d4bb3d6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sGGpgwE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsGGpgwE.jpg&h=7f13c4a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P5iGiK0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP5iGiK0.jpg&h=d6939a91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZtbQb41.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZtbQb41.jpg&h=483e55cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yG9usDn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyG9usDn.jpg&h=8ced4313&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mZdyUio.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmZdyUio.jpg&h=5541e918&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZZPY5p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZZPY5p4.jpg&h=d3219a0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KQuNYK5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnai